# Media: track ONLY the demo fixture; exclude everything else.
# App/public/videos/ and the non-fixture App/public/data/ dirs would otherwise
# stage copyright-derived renders. Deny-all, then re-allow the single fixture —
# the Sintel (CC BY 3.0) demo clip; see THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.
App/public/videos/*
!App/public/videos/sintel-blender-cc.mp4
App/public/data/*/
!App/public/data/sintel-blender-cc/
App/public/vibe.mp4

